<?xml version="1.0"?>
<config xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:magento:module:Magento_Config:etc/system_file.xsd">
    <system>
        <section id="carriers" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="320" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
            <group id="bring" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
                <label>Bring</label>
                <comment><![CDATA[Denne Bring modulen er utviklet av <a href="http://markant.no">Markant Norge AS</a>. Videredistribusjon av noe slag er ikke tillatt kun etter avtale med Markant.<br /><br />Kontakt oss om du har spørsmål rundt løsningen.<br />Epost: support@markant.no]]></comment>


                <group id="global" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="5" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
                    <label>Global</label>

                    <field id="bring_client_url" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="100" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Bring Client URL</label>
                        <comment>Your website domain.</comment>
                    </field>
                    <field id="mybring_client_uid" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="120" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Mybring login ID</label>
                    </field>
                    <field id="mybring_api_key" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="130" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Mybring login API key</label>
                    </field>
                </group>
                <group id="calculation" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="10" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
                    <label>Bring Shipping Guide</label>
                    <field id="active" translate="label" type="select" sortOrder="10" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Enabled</label>
                        <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                    </field>
                    <field id="title" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="20" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
                        <label>Title</label>
                    </field>

                    <field id="handling_type" translate="label" type="select" sortOrder="30" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Calculate Handling Fee</label>
                        <source_model>Magento\Shipping\Model\Source\HandlingType</source_model>
                    </field>
                    <field id="handling_fee" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="40" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Handling Fee</label>
                        <validate>validate-number validate-zero-or-greater</validate>
                    </field>


                    <field id="custom_method_prices" translate="label" sortOrder="60" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Custom Prices</label>
                        <frontend_model>Markant\Bring\Block\System\Config\Form\Field\CustomMethodPrice</frontend_model>
                        <backend_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Backend\Serialized\ArraySerialized</backend_model>
                        <comment>Add custom prices for each shipping method. You can base the prices on weight (Gram) and Country. These prices overrides the Automatic Shipping Prices.</comment>
                    </field>

                    <field id="activate_api" translate="label" type="select" sortOrder="65" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Activate Automatic Shipping Prices</label>
                        <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                        <comment><![CDATA[Bring's Shipping Guide will be used to add shipping methods and prices dynamically. Prices can be overridden with "Custom Prices".]]></comment>
                    </field>

                    <field id="show_estimated_delivery" translate="label" type="select" sortOrder="66" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Show estimated delivery time</label>
                        <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                        <depends>
                            <field id="activate_api">1</field>
                        </depends>
                    </field>

                    <field id="enabled_methods" translate="label" type="multiselect" sortOrder="66" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Enabled Bring Products</label>
                        <source_model>Markant\Bring\Model\Config\Source\BringMethod</source_model>
                        <can_be_empty>1</can_be_empty>
                        <depends>
                            <field id="activate_api">1</field>
                        </depends>
                    </field>


                    <field id="edi" translate="label" type="select" sortOrder="70" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>EDI</label>
                        <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                        <comment>Flag that tells if the parcel will be registred using EDI when it is shipped. Note that this flag may affect price and which products are available.</comment>
                        <depends>
                            <field id="activate_api">1</field>
                        </depends>
                    </field>
                    <field id="posting_at_post_office" translate="label" type="select" sortOrder="80" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Posting at post office</label>
                        <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                        <comment>Flag that tells whether the parcel is delivered at a post office when it is shipped. A surcharge will be applied for the following products: SERVICEPAKKE and BPAKKE_DOR-DOR (Bedriftspakke)</comment>
                        <depends>
                            <field id="activate_api">1</field>
                        </depends>
                    </field>
                    <field id="additional_services" translate="label" type="multiselect" sortOrder="90" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Additional Services</label>
                        <source_model>Markant\Bring\Model\Config\Source\AdditionalService</source_model>
                        <can_be_empty>1</can_be_empty>
                        <depends>
                            <field id="activate_api">1</field>
                        </depends>
                    </field>

                    <field id="enable_mybring" translate="label" type="select" sortOrder="110" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Enable Mybring</label>
                        <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                        <comment>If you are a Mybring user, you can authenticate requests to the Tracking API. Authenticated requests have the following benefits: You get more information about your parcels, for example signatures for proof of develiery. No rate limiting</comment>
                        <depends>
                            <field id="activate_api">1</field>
                        </depends>
                    </field>
                </group>

                <group id="booking" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="20" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
                    <label>Bring Booking</label>

                    <group id="package" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="20" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
                        <label>Standard package size</label>

                        <field id="width" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="20" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
                            <label>Width (cm)</label>
                        </field>
                        <field id="length" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="20" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
                            <label>Length (cm)</label>
                        </field>
                        <field id="height" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="20" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
                            <label>Height (cm)</label>
                        </field>
                    </group>
                </group>


                <field id="sort_order" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="140" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                    <label>Sort Order</label>
                </field>

            </group>
        </section>
    </system>
</config>